query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('dba',
'math',
'superuser',
'unix') AND t1.name IN ('area',
'compactness',
'expected-value',
'exponentiation',
'factorial',
'inner-product-space',
'microsoft-word',
'nonlinear-optimization',
'normed-spaces',
'operator-algebras',
'permissions',
'predicate-logic',
'sobolev-spaces',
'transformation')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100 group by t1.name;
